Occupying an elevated position just off Epping Road, 18 Orion Road is a 9 level office tower that has been maintained to the highest standards.

Current Availabilities:
+ Suite 3.01: 421.1 sqm - existing fit out includes: meeting rooms, boardroom, kitchen
+ Suite 3.02: 131.60 sqm  meeting room, balcony, kitchenette and existing workstations (can be combined with Suite 301)
+ Suite 7.04: 120 sqm  newly refurbished suite with workstations and office furniture
+ Suite 8.03: 218 sqm  training room, four meeting rooms and kitchen
+ Suite 8.04: 190.90 sqm boardroom, offices, kitchen and large corner balcony

18 Orion Road is located at the gateway to the Lane Cove Business Park within 250m of Epping Road. The building offers easy access to many locations around Sydney with Macquarie Park on your door step and North Sydney, Chatswood and St Leonards within a short distance. The M2 Freeway provides fast access around to Parramatta and Sydney's western suburbs.

18 Orion Road Lane Cove offers a range of superb office suites, all of which offer the highest standard of office accommodation in the area. Various suites and floors are available in sizes from 119sqm up to approximately 521sqm.

All areas have been extensively refurbished with fit out. Every suite in the building enjoys wonderful bushland and district views and most have large private balconies that ideal for staff break-out areas or client entertainment. There is also an on site child-care centre.
